'=============================================================================
' 关键调用关系（仅展示顶层/模块间调用）
'=============================================================================

note right of main
  ── ENTRY POINTS ──
  main → 无参数: upfs_session()
  main → --serve: serve_main()
  upfs_session → dispatch_command → 各 cmd_* 函数
  dispatch_command 根据命令名路由到对应处理函数
end note

note right of serve_main
  ── SERVER MODE ──
  serve_main → term_spawn → fork → upfs_session
  serve_main → api_spawn → fork → upfs_api_session
  ws_send/ws_recv 在 WebSocket 连接上转发终端 I/O
end note

note right of shell_mount
  ── MOUNT FLOW ──
  shell_mount → vfs_mount → upfs_mount_wrap → buf_init → fs_mount → journal_replay
  shell_mount → mem_init → proc_init → sched_init → env_init → proc_create_init
end note

note right of syscall_dispatch
  ── SYSCALL FLOW ──
  sched_tick → sched_run_slice → cpu_step → (SYSCALL) → syscall_dispatch → vfs_*/proc_* 等
  寄存器 R1-R3 传递参数, R0 存放返回值
end note

note right of codegen_emit
  ── COMPILER FLOW ──
  compile_c_to_asm → lexer_next (词法) → parser_parse (语法→AST)
  → codegen_emit (AST→汇编) → assemble_file (汇编→.upx)
end note

@enduml
